This paper is about video object segmentation using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also proposes a novel approach that involves a meta neural network, which could potentially fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with video processing (cs.MM) and optimization (cs.RO) techniques, which are also relevant sub-categories.
